best_platforms = games.query('platform == ["PS2","X360","PS3","Wii","DS","PS"]').pivot_table(
                                 index = ['year_of_release'], \
                                 columns = ['platform'],
                                 values = ['all_sales'],
                                 aggfunc =  ['sum'])

Самые популярные платформы (топ-5)¶

In [55]:
def top_5(groupby, region_sales, ax):
    pivot = new_games.groupby(groupby).agg({region_sales: 'sum'}).sort_values(by=region_sales)[:5]
    title_plot = {'na_sales': '   ', 'eu_sales': '  ', 
                  'jp_sales': '  '}
    color_plot = {'na_sales': 'slateblue', 'eu_sales': 'springgreen', 'jp_sales': 'coral'}
    plot = pivot.plot(kind='barh', edgecolor='black', title=title_plot[region_sales], ax=axes[ax], 
                   fontsize=14, color=color_plot[region_sales], rot=20, legend=None)
    plot.set_xlabel('')

    plot.grid(axis='x', alpha=0.5)

fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 3, figsize=(15, 6))
top_5('platform', 'na_sales', 0)
top_5('platform', 'eu_sales', 1)
top_5('platform', 'jp_sales', 2)
plt.tight_layout()  
plt.show()
